# CipherSQL Studio тАФ Data Flow Diagram (DFD)

## Level 0 тАФ Context Diagram

> The entire system as a single process, showing external entities and top-level data flows.

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    User(["ЁЯСд User (Browser)"])
    OpenAI(["ЁЯдЦ OpenAI / LLM API"])
    MongoDB[("ЁЯНГ MongoDB")]
    PostgreSQL[("ЁЯРШ PostgreSQL")]

    User -- "HTTP Requests\n(login, register, run SQL, get hint,\nview assignments, save attempt)" --> System["тЪЩя╕П CipherSQL Studio\n(Express API)"]
    System -- "JSON Responses\n(token, results, hints, assignments)" --> User
    System -- "Read/Write Users,\nAssignments, Attempts" --> MongoDB
    System -- "Execute SQL\n(schema-isolated)" --> PostgreSQL
    System -- "Hint Prompt" --> OpenAI
    OpenAI -- "AI Hint Text" --> System
```

---

## Level 1 тАФ System Decomposition

> The system broken into its five core processes.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    User(["ЁЯСд User"])

    subgraph Frontend["React Frontend"]
        AP["ЁЯУЛ Assignments Page\nuseAssignments hook"]
        ATE["ЁЯЦКя╕П Attempt Page\nSQL Editor + Panels"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Express Backend (port 5000)"]
        P1["1я╕ПтГг Auth\n/api/auth"]
        P2["2я╕ПтГг Assignments\n/api/assignments"]
        P3["3я╕ПтГг Execute SQL\n/api/execute"]
        P4["4я╕ПтГг Get Hint\n/api/hint"]
        P5["5я╕ПтГг Save/Get Attempts\n/api/attempts"]
    end

    DS1[("ЁЯНГ MongoDB\nUsers / Assignments / Attempts")]
    DS2[("ЁЯРШ PostgreSQL\nSchema-isolated tables")]
    DS3(["ЁЯдЦ OpenAI API"])

    User --> AP
    AP -- "GET /assignments" --> P2
    P2 -- assignment list --> AP
    AP -- "navigate to /attempt/:id" --> ATE

    ATE -- "GET /assignments/:id" --> P2
    P2 -- assignment detail --> ATE

    User -- "Register / Login" --> P1
    P1 -- "JWT Token" --> User
    P1 --> DS1

    ATE -- "POST /execute\n{assignmentId, query}" --> P3
    P3 --> DS2
    DS2 -- "columns, rows, rowCount, executionTime" --> P3
    P3 --> ATE

    ATE -- "POST /hint\n{assignmentId, currentQuery, errorMessage}" --> P4
    P4 -- "fetch Assignment from MongoDB" --> DS1
    P4 -- "buildHintPrompt тЖТ LLM call" --> DS3
    DS3 -- "hint text" --> P4
    P4 --> ATE

    ATE -- "POST /attempts\n{assignmentId, query, wasSuccessful}" --> P5
    P5 --> DS1
```

---

## Level 2 тАФ Detailed Process Flows

### 2.1 тАФ Authentication Flow (`/api/auth`)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U(["ЁЯСд User"])

    U -- "POST /api/auth/register\n{username, email, password}" --> V1{"Validate\nFields"}
    V1 -- "Missing fields / short password" --> E1["400 Error"]
    V1 -- "Valid" --> C1{"User\nexists?"}
    C1 -- "Yes" --> E2["400 User already exists"]
    C1 -- "No" --> H["bcrypt.hash(password, 10)"]
    H --> S["Save User to MongoDB\n{username, email, passwordHash}"]
    S --> T["jwt.sign({id, username})\nexpires: 24h"]
    T --> R1["201 {token, user{id,username,email}}"]

    U -- "POST /api/auth/login\n{email, password}" --> F{"Find User\nby email"}
    F -- "Not found" --> E3["400 Invalid credentials"]
    F -- "Found" --> BC{"bcrypt.compare\n(password, hash)"}
    BC -- "No match" --> E4["400 Invalid credentials"]
    BC -- "Match" --> T2["jwt.sign({id, username})"]
    T2 --> R2["200 {token, user}"]

    U -- "GET /api/auth/me\n[x-auth-token header]" --> MW["Auth Middleware\njwt.verify(token)"]
    MW -- "Invalid token" --> E5["401 Token not valid"]
    MW -- "Valid" --> DB["User.findById(id)\n.select('-passwordHash')"]
    DB --> R3["200 User object"]
```

---

### 2.2 тАФ SQL Execution Flow (`/api/execute`)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U(["ЁЯСд User"])

    U -- "POST /api/execute\n{assignmentId, query}" --> QV["queryValidator Middleware\nsanitizeQuery(query)"]
    QV -- "No query / dangerous SQL" --> E1["400 Error"]
    QV -- "sanitizedQuery attached to req" --> C["executeController"]

    C -- "Assignment.findById(assignmentId)" --> MDB[("MongoDB")]
    MDB -- "assignment.postgresSchema" --> SV{"Schema Name\nSafe? /^[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$/"}
    SV -- "Invalid" --> E2["500 Invalid schema configuration"]
    SV -- "Valid" --> PG["pool.connect()\nfrom PostgreSQL pool"]

    PG --> SP["SET search_path TO schema\nSET statement_timeout = 5000"]
    SP --> EX["client.query(sanitizedQuery)"]
    EX -- "Timeout > 5s" --> E3["400 Query timed out"]
    EX -- "SQL Error" --> E4["400 error.message"]
    EX -- "Success" --> R["200 {columns, rows, rowCount, executionTime}"]
    R --> U
```

---

### 2.3 тАФ AI Hint Flow (`/api/hint`)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U(["ЁЯСд User"])

    U -- "POST /api/hint\n{assignmentId, currentQuery, errorMessage}" --> HC["hintController"]
    HC -- "Assignment.findById(id)" --> MDB[("MongoDB")]
    MDB -- "assignment data" --> HC
    HC --> PB["buildHintPrompt(\n  assignment,\n  currentQuery,\n  errorMessage\n)"]
    PB --> OAI["openai.chat.completions.create\nmodel: gpt-4o-mini\nmax_tokens: 150"]
    OAI -- "hint text" --> R["200 {hint}"]
    OAI -- "API error" --> E["500 Failed to get hint"]
    R --> U
```

---

### 2.4 тАФ Assignments Flow (`/api/assignments`)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U(["ЁЯСд User"])

    U -- "GET /api/assignments" --> AC["assignmentController\ngetAllAssignments"]
    AC -- "Assignment.find()\n.select(title, description, difficulty, createdAt)" --> MDB[("MongoDB")]
    MDB --> R1["200 [ assignments ]"]
    R1 --> U

    U -- "GET /api/assignments/:id" --> AC2["assignmentController\ngetAssignmentById"]
    AC2 -- "Assignment.findById(id)" --> MDB
    MDB -- "null" --> E["404 Assignment not found"]
    MDB -- "document" --> R2["200 assignment object"]
    R2 --> U
```

---

### 2.5 тАФ Attempts Flow (`/api/attempts`)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U(["ЁЯСд User"])

    U -- "POST /api/attempts\n{assignmentId, query, wasSuccessful, errorMessage}" --> MW["Auth Middleware\n(optional тАФ userId nullable)"]
    MW --> SA["attemptController\nsaveAttempt"]
    SA -- "new Attempt({userId, assignmentId,\nquery, wasSuccessful, errorMessage})" --> MDB[("MongoDB")]
    MDB --> R1["201 attempt object"]
    R1 --> U

    U -- "GET /api/attempts/:userId\n[x-auth-token]" --> MW2["Auth Middleware\njwt.verify(token)"]
    MW2 -- "Invalid token" --> E1["401 Unauthorized"]
    MW2 --> AZ{"req.user.id\n=== userId?"}
    AZ -- "No" --> E2["403 Access denied"]
    AZ -- "Yes" --> GA["Attempt.find({userId})\n.populate('assignmentId')\n.sort(executedAt: -1).limit(100)"]
    GA --> R2["200 [ attempts ]"]
    R2 --> U
```

---

## Data Stores Reference

| Store | Technology | Collections / Schemas | Key Fields |
|---|---|---|---|
| `Users` | MongoDB | `users` | `username`, `email`, `passwordHash`, `createdAt` |
| [Assignments](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/frontend/src/services/api.js#12-13) | MongoDB | `assignments` | `title`, `description`, `difficulty`, `postgresSchema`, `tables`, `expectedColumns`, `hints` |
| [Attempts](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/backend/src/controllers/attemptController.js#28-46) | MongoDB | `attempts` | `userId` (ref User), `assignmentId` (ref Assignment), [query](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/backend/src/middleware/queryValidator.js#3-15), `wasSuccessful`, `errorMessage`, `executedAt` |
| SQL Practice Data | PostgreSQL | Per-assignment schemas (e.g. `ecommerce`, `library`) | Domain tables isolated per assignment via `search_path` |

---

## Frontend Component тЖТ API Mapping

| Frontend Component | Hook Used | API Called | Data Flowing |
|---|---|---|---|
| [AssignmentsPage](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/frontend/src/pages/AssignmentsPage.jsx#8-117) | `useAssignments` | `GET /api/assignments` | Assignment list (title, difficulty) |
| [AttemptPage](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/frontend/src/pages/AttemptPage.jsx#13-99) | direct [getAssignmentById](file:///d:/cipher-sql-studio/backend/src/controllers/assignmentController.js#12-23) | `GET /api/assignments/:id` | Full assignment (description, tables, hints) |
| `SQLEditor` + `ResultsPanel` | `useQueryExecution` | `POST /api/execute` | Query in тЖТ columns/rows/executionTime out |
| `HintPanel` | `useHint` | `POST /api/hint` | assignmentId+query+error тЖТ hint text |
| (implicit via hooks) | тАФ | `POST /api/attempts` | Query attempt saved to MongoDB |
